title: Frozen Warrior
description: Frozen Warrior Manhwa Cheok Ryugeom, a Goryeo swordsman, threw himself off a cliff holding the enemy for his master’s sake. However, he wakes up in the modern era—900 years later—after being frostbound… This is the revenge tale of Goryeo’s top swordsman in the modern era. The Frostbound Warrior • 냉동무사 • Kesatria Es
